id: pm-i7i4
title: "ADR: Git-native filesystem is the database (one file per item; no server, daemon, or DB engine)"
description: "Foundational data-model decision: the git working tree is the system of record."
type: Decision
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: adr,architecture,"area:storage",git-native
